# Archived: normalization 1898849 (do not apply the historical removal)

# This file used to record a unified diff that *removed* per-PR `concurrency`
# blocks from `.github/workflows/coderabbit-pr-automation-pr.yml` and
# `.github/workflows/coderabbit-pr-automation-manual.yml`.
#
# Applying that removal alone is unsafe when `CODERABBIT_AUTO_COMMIT` /
# `CODERABBIT_AUTO_PUSH` can be enabled: parallel runs on the same PR may race
# when pushing remediation commits.
#
# This repository keeps `concurrency` with `cancel-in-progress: true` on those
# workflows. Treat the old removal diff as superseded; if you normalize toward
# a shared template that omits concurrency, keep auto-commit/auto-push false
# by default or add an equivalent guard.
